# My Personal Blog Website

## Overview
This is a personal blog website created using HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript. The website features a home page with blog articles, a contact form, and responsive design.

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- GitHub Pages for deployment
- XAMPP for local development

## Features
- Responsive layout that adapts to different screen sizes (phones, tablets, desktops).
- Contact form with validation.
- Smooth animations and transitions for a better user experience.

## Getting Started Locally
1. Clone the repository to your local machine.
2. Open XAMPP Control Panel and start the Apache server.
3. Place the project folder in the `htdocs` directory of XAMPP.
4. Access the website by navigating to `http://localhost/your-project-folder` in your web browser.

## Deployment
This website is hosted on GitHub Pages. You can view it live at: [Your GitHub Pages URL](https://yourusername.github.io/your-repo-name)

